- Average CSS answers: {int(self.rubric.total_marks * 0.5)}-{int(self.rubric.total_marks * 0.65)} marks
- Only truly exceptional work reaches {int(self.STRICT_MAX_20_MARKS * 0.9)}-{self.STRICT_MAX_20_MARKS}
